I agree with the comments that this will certainly not make it easier for
the farmer. However food poisoning is only one aspect from the proposal,
proven zoonotic diseases as [those caused by _E. coli_, _Salmonella_,
_Campylobacter_, _Listeria_, [as well as tuberculosis, also come under
this heading. Diseases of which the zoonotic nature is not yet proven (like
BSE) may soon come in too.
--
